How to add a new web font
-------------------------

Whenever you add a font to this directory, run:

node app/blog/static/fonts/build

If you download font files from Google Fonts you can:

1. place font directory inside app/blog/static/fonts/data
2. use this tool: node app/blog/static/fonts/parse
3. copy the result to app/blog/static/fonts


